#fixtures(layout="column" ng-controller="AnyFixturesController as vm")
  .md-headline(
    layout="column" layout-align="start start"
    layout-gt-sm="row" layout-align-gt-sm="start center"
    flex
  )
    | I want to
    md-autocomplete(
      md-floating-label="do something..."
      md-autoselect="true"
      md-select-on-match="false" // Creates a jittery experience; we set the result manually for now
      md-no-cache="true" // For now we're querying local data so we don't need to cache
      md-delay="150" // 150 seems to be the right delay to feel responsive and avoid jitter
      md-selected-item="vm.fixture"
      md-search-text="vm.search_text"
      md-min-length="0" // Required to enable a dropdown with all the items
      md-items="fixture in vm.get_matches(vm.search_text)"
      md-item-text="fixture.name"
    )
      md-item-template
        span(md-highlight-text="vm.search_text") {{ fixture.name }}
    | every
    md-input-container
      label
        | frequency
      input(any-number type="number" name="frequency" ng-model="vm.fixture.frequency")
    | or so, days.

  .md-actions(layout="row" layout-align="end center")
    md-button(ng-click="vm.create_from_fixture()") Make It So
